⚠️ MANDATORY: If the article uses language indicating CHANGE or NEW DEVELOPMENT, include that in your pillar.

Example from a real article:
- Article says: "The offer was the closest Mr. Zelensky has come to addressing territorial disputes"
- ❌ BAD PILLAR: "Zelensky offered to create a demilitarized zone"
